A simple, multiplayer, board game which supports two players. Players move around the board and score points by revealing hidden food.
On a players turn, they can take one action: move or reveal. Players can steal food by revealing food of the
opposing color, causing the opponent to lose points. Player with the points at the end wins.

Players can join by going to `localhost:5000`.

Controls for red player:
    up: W
    down: D
    left: A
    right: S
    reveal: f

Controls for blue player:
    up: up arrow
    down: down arrow
    left: left arrow
    right: right arrow
    reveal: M

To install:
`pip install -r requirements.txt -e .`

To run the server:
`python app.py`